Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.44,0:02:25.99,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}相遇就是SHOCKWAVE！SHOCKWAVE！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:28.82,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}向着未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:30.99,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}开始前行
